Controls for ember - OGRE
This is a temporary file, when ember is more advanced the controls will be defined via the configuration service.

MOUSE: 
	left mouse to pick stuff
	right mouse switches between GUI and movement mode
	look around when not in game GUI mode
	point & click when in game GUI mode

W: walk forward
S: walk backwards
A: sidestep left
D: sidestep right

F7: switch between render modes
F8: take screenshot
F12: show debug console
